data.description: WELCOME HOME to this beautiful contemporary-style home with NO HOA! This spacious four-bedroom, two-bathroom residence offers over 1200+ square feet of comfortable living space. Situated on nearly an acre of land, the property is fully fenced for added privacy and security. Step inside and be greeted by a cozy living room with a charming brick wood-burning fireplace, perfect for those cozy evenings. The kitchen has been recently updated with new cabinets and appliances, providing a modern and functional space for culinary adventures. Throughout the entire house, you'll find tile flooring, adding a touch of elegance to every room. The bathrooms have also been tastefully updated, ensuring a fresh and stylish feel. Enjoy your backyard view in the comfort of your own covered and screened rear porch, which has been beautifully tiled. Additionally, the property features a concrete slab with a basketball ring, perfect for recreational activities. Also included with the property is a shed providing ample storage space. ALL MAJOR HOUSEHOLD ITEMS HAVE BEEN REPLACED! NEW WATER HEATER IN DECEMBER 2023. NEW ROOF IN MAY 2022, NEW DRAIN FIELD FOR SEPTIC TANK IN 2021. NEW DISHWASHER 2022. AIR CONDITIONING REPLACED IN 2020.Convenience is key, as this home offers easy access to shopping centers, colleges, public schools, medical facilities, and is also conveniently located near the Polk Parkway for seamless commuting to Tampa or Orlando. Don't miss out on this centrally located gem that combines modern updates, spacious living, and a convenient location. Schedule a showing today and make this house your new home!
